# Git rules

- [commitlint.config.js](mdc:commitlint.config.js)
- always commit in english
- Never commit automatically
- Write a commit message suggestion always that finish a prompt
- When user ask to create a new branch with the changes, use feature, fix, release, docs, hotfix prefixes and a short name after "/", like "feature/user-management" and automatically create a pull request with parent branch
